Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stasera mi sono proprio divertita!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anche io, tantissimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beh, buonanotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Notte!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'è qualcosa che non va?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La porta... non è chiusa a chiave...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:49.30,Cartello BASE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,0)\an7\blur1.3\bord0\shad0\fscx100\fscy100\pos(335.801,244.191)\p1\c&H994113&\1a&H7F&}m -102 -36 l 99 -36 99 5 -102 5
